\f0\b\fs24 Remember Window Positions and size
\b0  - MacWise will remember the size and position of your MacWise window when you close the window or quit and restart MacWise.\
	
\b Limit Screen Page Depth to 24 Lines
\b0  - Some host programs require the screen to scroll when the cursor is below the 24th line. If you are experiencing improper scrolling, then enable this option.\
Disable this option if you have a large monitor and want full page scrolling. \
Also, See "Previous Page Options" under the Edit menu for scrolling options.\

